snippet: Manchester United and Arsenal survived tough matches in the F.A. Cup, on Wednesday, each winning, 1-0, and advancing to the fourth round.
abstract: Manchester United and Arsenal survive rough matches to advance to fourth round of FA Cup; other soccer news noted.
